    "content": "-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n                            The Only Exception - Paramore\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nTabbed By: Valerie L\r\ne-mail: queefist@yahoo.com\r\nTuning: standard\r\n\r\nbass doesn't come in until 1:27\r\nfrom here he basically plays a descending E Major scale \r\nthen it goes back and forth very slowly\r\n\r\n[tab]G|9-8-6------------------------------|\r\nD|------9~--9~-9-7-6---------------9~|\r\nA|--------------------9~---7~--9~----|\r\nE|-----------------------------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab][Verse]\r\n\"and we've got to find other ways to make it alone.\"\r\nG|----------------------|  \r\nD|9~--9-7-6-------------| \r\nA|----------9~---7~---9-| \r\nE|----------------------| [/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------------------|\r\nD|9~---9~--9-7-6------6~--------|\r\nA|---------------9~-------7~--7-|\r\nE|------------------------------|x2[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab][Pre-Chorus]\r\n\"cause none of it was ever worth the risk\"\r\nG|-------------|\r\nD|-------------|\r\nA|-------------|\r\nE|0-0-0-0-0-0--|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab][Chorus]\r\n\"you are the only exception\" \r\nquarter notes\r\nG|------------------------------------|\r\nD|------4~------------------------2-1-|\r\nA|2-2-2----2-2-2-2~------------------4|\r\nE|------------------2-2-2-2~-0-0-0----|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------------------------|\r\nD|----4~------------------------------|\r\nA|2~-------2-2-2-2~-------------------|\r\nE|------------------2-2-2-2~-0-0-0-0~-|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------|\r\nA|4-4-4-4~-4-4-4-4~--2-2-2-2~------1/9-9-9|\r\nE|-----------------------------2-2--------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------6-4-6---------------------|\r\nA|4-4-4-4~--------4-4-4-2-2-2-2-------|\r\nE|-----------------------------2-2-2-2|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]\"i've got a tight grip of reality\"\r\nG|----------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------------------------------------|\r\nA|4-4-4-4~-4-4-4-4~--2-2-2-2~------1/9-9-9|\r\nE|-----------------------------2-2--------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------|\r\nD|----------6-4-6-----------------------|\r\nA|4-4-4-4~--------4-4-4-2-2-2-2~--------|\r\nE|-------------------------------2-2-2-2|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------------|\r\nD|---------------|\r\nA|----------1/7~-|\r\nE|0-0-0-0-0------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab][Outro chorus]\r\n\"you are the only exception..\"\r\nG|---------------------------------|\r\nD|----4~-----------------------2-1-|\r\nA|2~-------2~---4-2---------------4|\r\nE|-------------------2~--2--0~-----|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|------------------------------------------------|\r\nD|-------4~---------------------------------------|\r\nA|2~---2-----------------------------------0~---7~|\r\nE|----------2~---2~--0~---5~---5~--0~--0~---------|[/tab]\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n************************************\r\n\r\n| /  slide up\r\n| ~  vibrato\r\n\r\n************************************",
